      <component type='text' id='instructiontext123'> 
         <text variable='true' translate='true'><![CDATA[This demo depicts the behavior of packets as they pass through hubs.  Start the demo by selecting Activity and pressing the <i>Send</i> button.<br><br>You may replay the demo by selecting the <i>Reset</i> button and then selecting the <i>Send</i> button.<br><br>Answer each question by selecting the question button and choosing the correct answer.  You may get feedback by selecting the <i>Grade</i> button.]]></text> 
      </component>
       <!-- question #1 text -->
              <component type='text' id='q1stemt'>
                <!-- note use of "do not translate" tag -->
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[In this network, if a PC (the source PC) connected to HubA sends a message to another PC (the destination PC), also connected to HubA, which devices will receive the message?]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q1o1t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[The destination PC only]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q1o2t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to HubA only.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q1o3t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to HubA and HubB, but HubB will not forward the message any further.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q1o4t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to every hub on the network.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <!-- question #2 text -->
            <component type='text' id='q2stemt'>
                <!-- note use of variable -->
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[In this network, if a PC (the source PC) connected to a HubA sends a message to another PC (the destination PC) connected to HubB, which devices will receive the message?]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q2o1t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[The destination PC only.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q2o2t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to HubB only.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q2o3t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to HubA and the destination PC on HubB only.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q2o4t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to HubA and all PCs connected to HubB only.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
             <component type='text' id='q2o5t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[All PCs connected to every hub on the network.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <!-- question #3 text -->
            <component type='text' id='q3stemt'>
                <!-- note use of variable -->
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[What occurs if two devices send information across the network at the same time?]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q3o1t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[The host devices will send the messages simultaneously, but the two frames will collide and the devices must retransmit the message at a random interval]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q3o2t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[The host devices will send the messages simultaneously, but the hub will maintain two separate conversational paths and the messages will be passed to the correct destination devices.]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q3o3t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[The hub will not allow multiple devices to send message simultaneously, therefore each device must wait for the hub to request the message]]>
                </text>
            </component>
            <component type='text' id='q3o4t'>
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
                    <![CDATA[The hub will not allow multiple devices to send messages simultaneously, therefore each device must send a “request to transmit” frame to the hub]]>
                </text>
            </component>
			 <!-- question #4 text -->
            <component type='text' id='q4stemt'>
                <!-- note use of variable -->
                <text variable='false' translate='false'>
